author: Julia Musto
title: Mark Cuban on reopening economy: Biggest challenge right now is asymptomatic carriers of COVID-19
description: The ultimate challenge posed by the coronavirus pandemic right now is asymptomatic carriers of the virus, billionaire businessman and Dallas Mavericks owner Mark Cuban said Thursday.
